{"tid":579544,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"大家入嚟傾吓本地Hip Hop","createTime":"2018-03-03T16:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T18:07:11.000Z","uid":149118,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8158809cc6e1126bcad9682161d250bcbd03e549","tid":579544,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"個人認為Bakerie 早班火車呢首歌好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然可能冇乜人識佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我覺得大家一定要聽下呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前嚟過我學校表演不過嗰陣時唔識佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次老佛爺香港站我都有去<br />\n我覺得佢哋應該要紅過啲香港嘅主流歌星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6SvD5pA33Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6SvD5pA33Ew&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7e5c6ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6SvD5pA33Ew</a><br />\n睇埋紀錄片了解下佢地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6nsaz4MoPJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6nsaz4MoPJA&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7d5dfc56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6nsaz4MoPJA</a><br />\n佢哋其他歌都好正 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2uMsrsMeGUE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2uMsrsMeGUE&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e0d79094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2uMsrsMeGUE</a><br />\n當然仲有刀哥呢首<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VJIM8y9dJNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVJIM8y9dJNs&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=de8a8826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VJIM8y9dJNs</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋大家可以聽下米奇老味同埋米奇老味嘅奶油包d歌<br />\n個人最鐘意呢首<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pxmfaJsKibI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpxmfaJsKibI&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=882ce134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pxmfaJsKibI</a><br />\n奶油包<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iBE4eRbbcVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiBE4eRbbcVE&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ad07e287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iBE4eRbbcVE</a><br />\n奶油包 freestyle <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KWGK9YrLWBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKWGK9YrLWBg&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c6f2dcbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KWGK9YrLWBg</a><br />\n<br />\nYoung queenz 個人認為呢首叫ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F2pErtCrj5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF2pErtCrj5g&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHn57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=78c63331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F2pErtCrj5g</a><br />\n希望大家可以支持下香港hip hop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef858b613f5f05d901597dda44be434b9b7b3217","tid":579544,"uid":149118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"da798a721f5a919e7fd3474f8e964f522a294939","tid":579544,"uid":42349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"555232ab89ab9f2c7d58a22bdc42e0e5b243af5a","tid":579544,"uid":58335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T17:34:35.000Z","msg":"翡翠 ya ya<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" 